name: AstarPrince
description: AstarPrince is the first Prince NFT collection on Astar Network. AstarPrince is not just another PFP project, but it comes with many utilities and holder benefits planned ahead! Our ultimate mission is to support promising projects on Astar Network by providing our creative resources. The art is CC0(Creative Common zero), which means you will own all rights to the NFT you mint/buy. This will allow you or any projects to use AstarPrince brand and help create AstarPrince ecosystem.
